dc_title_s: Topographical plan of the river Meganatawan by A. Murray Esqr.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. G. Matthews, Lith., Montreal. 1 map on var. sheets; sheets 63 x 95 cm. or smaller. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
